IDUNA is a four piece alternative rock group based out of Toronto, Ontario.

Picking up on the sensibilities of Matt Good, Smashing Pumpkins, and other serious rock acts of the past three decades, their music ranges from heavy and soulful to high energy rock and roll exploring a wide range of melodic flourishes and dynamic flux.
